00:19:17,134 --> 00:19:24,437
[SPEAKER_01]: So if there was just a mishap with respect to scheduling, and I certainly understand everyone's doing the best they can,

198
00:19:25,617 --> 00:19:41,490
[SPEAKER_01]: You certainly have a lot of schedules to figure out with respect to the public body's business, but generally an emergency is limited to natural disasters, public health matters, and public safety issues.

