00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:43,131
[SPEAKER_01]: So something to be aware of.

200
00:19:44,252 --> 00:19:53,039
[SPEAKER_01]: We can talk a little bit about if something's unanticipated, that's a little bit different, but hosting is really limited in the emergency context.

