00:21:47,525 --> 00:21:53,288
[SPEAKER_01]: members as well as members of the public indicating that the meeting was going to be recorded.

216
00:21:53,308 --> 00:21:59,632
[SPEAKER_01]: In my opinion, the chair can decide to reasonably regulate the recording placement.

217
00:22:00,092 --> 00:22:07,316
[SPEAKER_01]: Obviously, as technology is smaller and smaller, this is less of an issue, but we don't want to block anyone's view, so to speak.

