00:28:48,781 --> 00:28:50,442
[SPEAKER_01]: You know, like I said, 10, 15 minutes

276
00:28:52,043 --> 00:29:00,451
[SPEAKER_01]: is usually what I see, but there are some meetings where warrants particular input from members of the public.

