00:30:13,336 --> 00:30:15,578
[SPEAKER_01]: They're not on the meeting agenda itself.

288
00:30:16,218 --> 00:30:28,008
[SPEAKER_01]: And so it may be something that you decide to put on a future meeting agenda so that members of the public that may be interested in the topic can come to the next meeting and say, okay, this is going to be reviewed.

